OL,5, A US zoo has apologised for mistreating
OL,6, a kiwi, after footage of visitors      
OL,7, patting the nocturnal bird under bright
OL,8, lights caused outrage in New Zealand.  
OL,10,FZoo Miami said it was "deeply sorry"   
OL,11,Fabout the incident, which occurred     
OL,12,Fduring a paid animal encounter between 
OL,13,Fthe kiwi and zoo guests.               
OL,15,FThe kiwi encounter has since been      
OL,16,Fremoved from the zoo's offerings.      
